title: 17 people reveal the telltale signs they’re getting older (17 Photos)
text:
View as Slideshow 1 
We all have that moment when we discover that we’re no longer part of the cool and hip generation. 17 year olds start educating us on things, partying sounds like not that great of a time and the highlight of your week is a two-for-one coupon on kitchen sponges. Whatever it is that triggers your inner-realization, once it happens there’s no going back. 2
